sql:
SELECT technology_name
FROM technologies
ORDER BY technology_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
'biggest climate change impacts' refers to the highest comparison results for each battery type in the climate change category;
the comparison results are ordered in descending order;
the comparison results are used as a measure of climate change impact;
climate change category is one of the categories in the lci_methods table, indicating that the method measures climate change impacts.

sql:
SELECT AVG(report_count) AS average_reports_per_user
FROM (
  SELECT user_id, COUNT(report_id) AS report_count
  FROM reports
  GROUP BY user_id
) AS user_report_counts;
